snippet.title: Buddhist Monk Died for 3 Days and Came Back (After Life Experience)

localized.description:
This is one of the great testimony! Pyan Shinthaw Paulu was born in Myanmar. He became a Buddisht monk. At age of 21, he had yellow fever and malaria. Because of complication of his illness, he died and went to hell. He found out the most respectable person was in hell. He also met Peter and he got message from Peter in heaven.

To see more videos of heaven and hell visitation,
http://www.heavenvisit.com
